ViaFo,provides,a,range,of,solutions,for,mobile,developers,that,allow,them,to,add,services,such,as,Twitter,and,Facebook,in,their,apps,Viafo,s,Services,Gateway,takes,popular,actions,such,as,share,upload,check,in,local,search,and,tags,and,unifies,them,across,the,major,services,For,consumers,the,service,lets,them,aggregate,all,RSS,news,and,social,networking,feeds,onto,their,mobile,device,For,enterprises,ViaFo,solutions,allow,mobile,access,to,services,from,a,dedicated,client,The,API,gives,developers,access,to,the,functionality,of,the,ViaFo,Services,Gateway,It,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,JSON